Package: chatalot
Title: Process a Lot of Chats
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Process a lot of large language model chats with 'ellmer'.
    Provides both sequential and parallel processing of chat interactions
    with features including tool calling and structured data extraction.
    Enables workflow persistence through checkpoint and resume. 
    Additional quality-of-life features include sound notifications and
    verbosity options. Parallel processing is implemented using 'future'.
    Includes methods for retrieving progress status, chat texts, and chat objects.
